WEBVTT

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:30.496
And just as Jenner's discovery
opened the door

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:32.800
for all of the vaccines
that followed after,

00:04:33.800 --> 00:04:37.376
the drugs we've discovered
open the possibility of a whole new field:

00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:39.880
preventative psychopharmacology.

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:43.296
But whether that's 15 years away,

00:04:43.320 --> 00:04:45.416
or 150 years away,

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:47.456
depends not just on the science,

00:04:47.480 --> 00:04:50.560
but on what we as a society
choose to do with it.

00:04:51.320 --> 00:04:52.536
Thank you.

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:56.000
(Applause)